@startuml

"Data Source" -> "Data Source\nAdapter" : sends data\n(over e.g. MQTT)
"Data Source\nAdapter" -> Aggregator : forwards data
Aggregator -> DB : stores data
"Permission\nScheduler" -> Streamer : creates streamers\nfor permissions
Aggregator -> Streamer : forwards filtered and processed data
Streamer <-> EP : streams data\nover MQTT

@enduml